Soulless unarmoured zombies may occasionally appear near the chaotic rift north of Draynor Village during the 2018 Halloween event. They will be summoned by the soulless necromancer if he is not defeated quickly enough. Despite having an attack option, they cannot be attacked directly.

Attempting to attack them results in the following message:

This zombie doesn't have a soul! Restore it so that Death can take him down!

To defeat them, the player must siphon souls from Death's soul rift to make them mortal.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • The examine quote is a reference to the lyrics of the song Lose Yourself by Eminem.
